    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This car is in pristine condition\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken meticulous care of it, always kept it garaged, and there\u2019s not a single blemish to be found. It drives like a dream and is ready for a new home. You seriously won't find one cleaner than this! Feel free to reach out with any questions! \u2728",
