    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in a climate-controlled garage and maintained with obsessive attention to detail. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster thanks to a professional ceramic coating and remains entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the leather remains supple with zero creasing on the bolsters, and every button and switchgear provides that crisp, tactile click found only in showroom-fresh examples. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history with all maintenance performed exclusively by certified specialists. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, it performs exactly as it did the day it was delivered. No modifications, no accidents, and no excuses\u2014this is a concours-level example for the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 44500.0,
